OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy and mostly cloudy
OL,6,Fthroughout the day as outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain move east, these heavy at times.
OL,8,FStaying driest and brightest towards
OL,9,FEast Lothian and Berwickshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly cloudy through the
OL,12,Fevening with outbreaks of rain,
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy at first. Further
OL,14,Frain the in the east overnight, drier
OL,15,Fand clearer spells will develop in the
OL,16,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
