OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FRain in the east at first will
OL,6,Fgradually clear. Otherwise bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells and a few showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping during the day, these heavy
OL,9,Fat times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,FTuesday and Wednesday, some heavy and
OL,14,Fthundery. Widespread cloud and rain
OL,15,Farriving from the west on Thursday.
